<td>
<div align="center"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-large;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img class="__mce_add_custom__" title="Need Assistance?" src="http://www.scuffz.com/product_images/uploaded_images/need-help-skateboards.jpg" alt="Guide for ordering skateboards" width="750" height="269" /></span></strong></span>
